/h48SI2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F07%2F29%2Fh48SI2.png&h=8276f73a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n五毛狗毛澤東真係賤種仆街黎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請注意,五毛狗毛潤之#90863竟然恥笑陳浩天無膽量俾人拉，個post 仲要得佢一班五毛同事幫推<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/760904\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/760904</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ec8addaa659e4602c2d4c55319ed3840eb385bf6","tid":800991,"uid":3117,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T15:33:06.000Z","msg":"請大家無視黃巢同人生鍾嘉欣兩隻五毛狗"},{"pid":"6d6d1ace9a4e1f230b9508eb77588d3e82a03506","tid":800991,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T15:33:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/gMwecxrqCBg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FgMwecxrqCBg&d=shnVi3qh%2BggJmGL%2Bp7zlEIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=3bc0af4a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/gMwecxrqCBg</a>"}]}